      "writtenOn": "2017-10-24T15:11:47Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "So right now the majority of tasks (test, perf, upload, infra, normal housekeeper, etc) will have one associated job.  Build tasks may have several, and the BundleRecipes and Isolate* tasks will have ~80 or so.  I really want Task.Jobs to be a slice.  I changed to use sort.SearchStrings.  I\u0027m hoping we don\u0027t need a map or util.StringSet for now.",
      "parentUuid": "3d81e7ec_ee302f31",
